    "English": "Overloads the energy beam generated by the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Blaze Javelin</span>, causing it to deliver a power electrical charge at its point of impact.<br><br>Will briefly <span class=\"name name-stellar\">stun</span> any organic and inorganic entities that intersect the Blaze Javelin's beam.",
